{
  "stem": "802.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Even though we're not religious, our sense of Jewishness was very profound, you know, and very intact.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something like it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Something to cover that wall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day, somebody, I think it was a Ukrainian, to whom it occurred that it was strange that all the rooms on that particular wall had a large piece of furniture, like a chifferobe.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he became very suspicious, and he wanted to uncover this wall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there were Jewish policemen in the Warsaw Ghetto, some of whom were not very nice.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted to save their lives, you know, but they did not constitute a majority.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would say they constituted probably a minority.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this man's family, ironically enough, was hiding with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He couldn't even save his family, you see?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he bought that Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He gave him a watch or some gold, and he let us-- you know, he did not move away the wardrobe, the chifferobe.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- let me just-- the houses and the buildings in Poland had a courtyard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if you're familiar with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's a courtyard and four buildings that, you know, it's a square.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, an interior courtyard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the building next to ours, in the courtyard-- we lived in the courtyard-- there was a family who was also hiding the way we were hiding, and they were discovered there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took them out, and they shot them all but for one boy, who was about eight years old.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is very significant, because I'll tell you something about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They shot his parents in front of his eyes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, you know, we used to hide there all the time, whenever there was a raid, you know, whenever there was a roundup.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
